00:51:02,930 --> 00:51:06,640
It's not even a time where all citizens need to fight with their lives on the line.

582
00:51:07,640 --> 00:51:10,910
You aren't desperate and it isn't your belief either.

583
00:51:12,800 --> 00:51:17,920
To me, you are my belief and my world.

584
00:51:20,050 --> 00:51:23,260
So I'll do all the things you do out of your belief.

585
