No, it's about movies.

592
00:52:01,040 --> 00:52:02,910
Also...

593
00:52:07,090 --> 00:52:09,620
We are dating as of today.

594
00:52:35,160 --> 00:52:40,970
Sunbae used to be my side, my belief...

595
00:52:42,490 --> 00:52:45,050
and my world.

596
00:52:55,440 --> 00:53:00,520
Your belief is no longer of this world.

