I don't know if we'll be able to do well.

608
00:53:52,190 --> 00:53:55,230
Don't worry. You know it best, after all.

609
00:53:55,230 --> 00:53:58,030
What it is that people want.

610
00:53:58,030 --> 00:53:59,790
Should I take some cheongsimhwan? 
