00:53:59,790 --> 00:54:02,750
Now that they suddenly want to talk,

612
00:54:02,750 --> 00:54:05,260
I feel more nervous.

613
00:54:05,260 --> 00:54:10,060
I heard that the new vice president is even more vicious.

614
00:54:12,250 --> 00:54:17,080
Even so, they say that he isn't a bad person. They say he's smart and logical.

615
00:54:17,080 --> 00:54:22,000
It's worrisome because he's smart. We don't know what kind of tricks he'll play.

616
00:54:22,000 --> 00:54:26,510
On top of that, since he's the chairman's son-in-law, he's definitely going to be on the company's side.

617
00:54:26,510 --> 00:54:29,890
Even so, this is a great improvement.

618
00:54:29,890 --> 00:54:32,840
Before, they wouldn't even meet with us.

619
00:54:32,840 --> 00:54:35,190
It'll turn out well. The world has changed a lot too.

620
00:54:35,190 --> 00:54:37,270
It should be like that, right?

621
00:54:37,270 --> 00:54:40,060
Okay, then let's go and get just one drink somewhere.

622
00:54:40,060 --> 00:54:42,660
I think that's the only way I'll be able to fall asleep.

623
00:54:48,210 --> 00:54:49,920
You're going to negotiate with them?

624
00:54:49,920 --> 00:54:52,580
Who said you could? You're just bypassing me, the CEO?

625
00:54:52,580 --> 00:54:55,920
Didn't you tell me to do whatever I want?

626
00:54:55,920 --> 00:54:58,690
Was being in there for four years the problem?

627
00:54:58,690 --> 00:55:00,150
Why are you doing things you normally don't do?

628
00:55:00,150 --> 00:55:04,460
The process is just for formality;  the result won't change.

629
00:55:04,460 --> 00:55:08,450
Report every detail of the result of the negotiation to me.

630
00:55:08,450 --> 00:55:12,640
Okay, I'm going to go out for some air.

631
00:55:19,560 --> 00:55:23,610
- Ji Soo. 
- Yes?

632
00:55:23,610 --> 00:55:31,040
I don't think that we're going to win.

633
00:55:31,040 --> 00:55:35,350
Even so, I'm not going to lose easily.

634
00:55:36,640 --> 00:55:42,670
Whether you win or lose, I'll be on your side until the end.

